    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years old and older

          -  Hilar and/or mediastinal lymphadenopathy (&gt; 1 cm on the short axis, as assessed by
             contrast-enhanced CT scan (computed tomography))

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Uncontrolled coagulopathy

          -  Refusal to sign informed consent
      </textblock>
